    "description": "Takano Co.,Ltd. manufactures and sells office chairs and other office furniture, springs, exterior products, electronics-related products, and equipment for health and welfare in Japan and internationally. The company offers medical and healthcare equipment, including stretchers, wheelchairs, wheelchair cushions, walking aids, and others; exterior products comprising awnings, parasols, and multi-utility room products; office furniture, such as swivel chairs and conference room chairs; and health food products. It also provides solenoid actuators, including electromagnetic electrical components for various industrial equipment; spring and unit components comprising precision, wiring, and spiral springs; automatic optical inspection and measurement systems, such as LCD panel inspection system, battery-related material, and Web inspection systems; and in vitro diagnostic reagent. The company was formerly known as Takano Factory Co.,Ltd and changed its name to Takano Co.,Ltd. in 1973. Takano Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1941 and is headquartered in Kamiina, Japan."
